:: Case Study: MA RAINEY'S BLACK BOTTOM [nobr]
<h1>"Skin and Air": Remediation and Power in <i>Ma Rainey's Black Bottom</i></h1>
<figure>
	<video controls>
	<source src="assets/videos/mrbb.mp4" type="video/mp4">
