	</figure>
	<figure>
		<img style="width:100%" @src=[_slides[2]]>
		<figcaption>The set for the Writer's Theater 2019 production of the play. Note the conspicuous speaker that allows Irvin and Sturdyvant to give their orders without leaving the control room. <br>Photo by Michael Brosilow courtesy of New City Stage.</figcaption>
	</figure>
	<figure>
		<img style="width:100%" @src=[_slides[1]]>
