<p>In EndlessGame, four default avatars (vaguely masculine bodies with blank faces named Alpha; vaguely female bodies named Beta were also available), colored to follow Beckett‚Äôs script, execute the code written for Beckett‚Äôs dancers. It‚Äôs not the first [[digital adaptation of Quad->Digital Adaptations of Quad]] that‚Äôs been made, but it is the first one to be made in <<define "Unity" "Unity">> or to run in <<define "virtual reality" "Virtual Reality">>. </p>

